					<p>
				<h2><a href="http://www.abominable.cc/2012/12/26/a-christmas-carol/" rel="bookmark" title="A Christmas Carol">Comic Notes</a></h2>
				<div class="entry">
					<p>Happy Holidays, everyone!<br />
&nbsp;</p>
				</div>

				<div class="postmeta-featured">
					<a href="http://www.abominable.cc/2012/12/26/a-christmas-carol/#comments" title="Comment on A Christmas Carol"><span class="postmeta-comments">12 Comments <img src="/images/site/balloons-button.png"></span></a>
